      "description": "Prepare to be impressed by this absolute gem! This car is in pristine, mint condition and looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor. Every detail has been meticulously maintained, offering a flawless driving experience and a spotless interior. If you're looking for perfection on wheels, this is the one for you!",
