    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and will require significant attention from its next owner. The exterior shows noticeable wear, including several deep scratches, fading paint, and some rust spots on the lower panels. Mechanically, the engine runs but has a persistent leak and the transmission shifts roughly, suggesting major service or a rebuild may be necessary soon. The interior also shows its age with torn upholstery and some non-functional electronics. It is a solid candidate for a full restoration or a parts car for someone with the right tools and time.",
